libvortex-1.1:
* [fix] Updated web-socket module to use new nopoll_conn_set_on_close
  call to control when socket is closed at the noPoll layer to avoid closing
  it after at the vortex layer with the risk of closing a different socket but
  with the same value. 

* [fix] Updated WebSocket connection API to include a new function to get 
  noPollCtx. API added:

  - vortex_websocket_connection_get_ctx

* [fix] Updated vortex-regression-client.c to include more debug information about
  errors found..

 

