  manner so first initialization lock is released using PyEval_SaveThread but
  the rest of the cases PyGILState_Ensure is used.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r2558 | francis.brosnan.bl.zquez | 2013-05-11 18:25:49 +0000 (Sat, 11 May 2013) | 4 lines

