  the lock just after the entier python init was completed.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r2557 | francis.brosnan.bl.zquez | 2013-05-06 19:11:30 +0000 (Mon, 06 May 2013) | 5 lines

turbulence:
* [fix] Updated mod-python to avoid calling to acquire GIL but instead use
  thread init and release lock calls. Fixes some issues while calling to python 
  APIs that acquires and releases the GIL explicitly.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r2556 | francis.brosnan.bl.zquez | 2013-05-06 19:08:48 +0000 (Mon, 06 May 2013) | 4 lines

