  connection module. 

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r2491 | francis.brosnan.bl.zquez | 2013-04-01 18:58:25 +0000 (Mon, 01 Apr 2013) | 22 lines

turbulence:
* [new] Global engine update to allow supporting in a general
  manner proxing BEEP connection on the master process so they
  are handled transparently at the child process as if it were
  received directly by them. 

  This new support has been added to bypass the limitations of 
  OpenSSL in terms to saving SSL context and recovering it at a 
  child process. 

  With this new support mod-websocket is able to work on master 
  and child processes (using reuse=yes configuration). 
  NICE!!! Still more work is required to update regression 
  tests and cleanup the code.

  API added:
  - turbulence_conn_mgr_proxy_on_parent

* [new] Updated turbulence code to install a vortex log handler
  when debug isn't enabled on that library to track all critical
  errors found and display them as turbulence error() messages.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r2490 | francis.brosnan.bl.zquez | 2013-04-01 11:41:40 +0000 (Mon, 01 Apr 2013) | 7 lines

libvortex-1.1:
* [new] Updated vortex support module API to include a new function
  to create a portable pipe. Moved this code from lua code which now
  uses this public and cleaned definition. API added:

   - vortex_support_pipe

