r2476 | francis.brosnan.bl.zquez | 2013-03-19 18:18:53 +0000 (Tue, 19 Mar 2013) | 8 lines

libvortex-1.1:
* [fix] Updated vortex_support.c to replace GetEnvironmentVariable 
  and SetEnvironmentVariable with they "A" implementations to ensure
  ascii version is used even when those functions are used with Unicode
  build enabled. Bug reported and fix proposed by Étienne Dupuis (Thanks!)
  More information at:
  http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/windows/desktop/dd317766(v=vs.85).aspx

