r2306 | francis.brosnan.bl.zquez | 2011-12-12 09:28:28 +0000 (Mon, 12 Dec 2011) | 6 lines

libvortex-1.1:
* [fix] Making vortex.Ctx.new_event to flag event period
  with "l" instead of "i" to avoid OverflowError: signed 
  integer is greater than maximum.


