  connections on childs when turbulence is in process of finishing..

* [fix] Several updates to mod-python to remove Py_Finalize calls.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r2196 | francis.brosnan.bl.zquez | 2011-09-14 10:17:46 +0000 (Wed, 14 Sep 2011) | 4 lines

libvortex-1.1:
* [fix] Fixed PyVortex handling to detect pvalue == NULL after calling
  PyErr_Fetch, so it points to Py_None.

