r2195 | francis.brosnan.bl.zquez | 2011-09-14 06:43:49 +0000 (Wed, 14 Sep 2011) | 4 lines

turbulence:
* [fix] Removed call to Py_Finalize from mod_python (is causing lot of
  problems on termination..).

