  handlers). 

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r2135 | francis.brosnan.bl.zquez | 2011-08-09 18:08:16 +0000 (Tue, 09 Aug 2011) | 14 lines

libvortex-1.1:
* [fix] Moved vortex ctx cleanup code to be run at vortex_exit_ctx
  to avoid circular references problems (calling that releases references
  is not run until the last vortex_ctx_unref which will never happen).
  Checked regression tests to ensure everything keeps working (especially
  pull api).

* [new] Added new function to allow uninstall ctx cleanup function 
  from vortex ctx API.

* [fix] Fixed bug at pull API which was causing to not release all events
  once finished vortex context (vortex_exit_ctx). Added regression test to
  reproduce bug and check fix introduced (test-14-e).

