  actual remote peer IP. Unlike vortex_connection_get_host which returns the
  connecting name (that may be not an IP) this new function ensures returning
  an IP. Updated PyVortex to also support this addition:

   - vortex_connection_get_host_ip
   - vortex.Connection.host_ip

