r1812 | francis.brosnan.bl.zquez | 2010-06-06 17:40:35 +0000 (Sun, 06 Jun 2010) | 16 lines

libvortex-1.1:
* [fix] General updates inside vortex channel module to implement
  seqno tracking using two values (ackno + reference) instead of 
  a maximum value which is problematic for continuous transfer
  (exceeding 4GB limit). 

* [fix] Added several alloc checks inside channel module.

* [fix] Updated vortex sequencer to check values returned by
  next frame size handler installed, closing the connection in
  case of failures.

* [fix] Updated vortex frame module to use new incoming seq no
  check implemented.
  

