r1674 | francis.brosnan.bl.zquez | 2010-01-28 07:17:35 +0000 (Thu, 28 Jan 2010) | 6 lines

libvortex-1.1:
* [fix] Finally finished out of order reply handling for different/parallel
  ANS/NUL replies over the same channel. Updated regtest test_03-c to reproduce
  and check fix introduced. Still more work required to better test current
  function.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r1673 | francis.brosnan.bl.zquez | 2010-01-27 13:14:12 +0000 (Wed, 27 Jan 2010) | 9 lines

libvortex-1.1:
* [fix] Rewritten channel serialize code to be seqno based
  rather msgno and frame type. This solves some issues with
  heavily loaded frame handlers that causes some NUL frames
  (stored as -1) to be missed. Also fixed connection dealloc
  failures when channel serialize is enabled and ANS/NUL frames
  are received. Added reg test test_03c to reproduce the
  problem and check fix introduced.

