r1103 | francis.brosnan.bl.zquez | 2008-12-24 18:28:05 +0000 (Wed, 24 Dec 2008) | 11 lines

libaxl:
* [new] Added nested <![CDATA[]]> support by doing some particular 
  entity substitutions. This will ensure that an xml document using
  CDATA decl can hold any binary data. Added support functions 
  for additional operations around this feature. API added:

    - axl_node_has_invalid_chars_cdata
    - axl_node_content_copy_and_escape_cdata

  Added regression test (test_42).

