libvortex:
* [fix] web updates.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r1087 | francis.brosnan.bl.zquez | 2008-12-08 21:31:42 +0000 (Mon, 08 Dec 2008) | 9 lines

libvortex-1.1:
* [new] Added two new events to handle incoming connection event and connection
  closed event. API added:
  
   - VORTEX_EVENT_CONNECTION_CLOSED
   - VORTEX_EVENT_CONNECTION_ACCEPTED

  Updated regression tests (test 14 series).

