r991 | francis.brosnan.bl.zquez | 2008-10-22 08:09:35 +0000 (Wed, 22 Oct 2008) | 9 lines

libvortex:
* [fix] Updated error handling on TLS implementation to show full error stack
  provided by OpenSSL (the proper manner to debug TLS failures). Applied change
  to 1.0/1.1

* [fix] Disabled SEQ frame generation during TLS negotiation to avoid producing
  noise in the middle of the connection reset. Applied change to 1.0/1.1


