------------------------------------------------------------------------
r789 | francis.brosnan.bl.zquez | 2008-04-14 16:21:29 +0000 (Mon, 14 Apr 2008) | 15 lines

libvortex:
* [fix] Fixed wrong internal handling for reply sent on a channel
  which wasn't checking if the reply sent was complete causing to
  signal more replies sent than actual value. Updated regression test
  to reproduce and check this problem that was causing a peer to 
  not be able to close a connection after sending huge replies.
  Fixed introduced in 1.0 and 1.1. Problem reported by Mihail
  Dmitrievsky.

* [new] Moving from internal API to the public the following 
  function that allows to wait if all replies were sent for a
  particular channel. API added:

   - vortex_channel_block_until_replies_are_sent

