r753 | francis.brosnan.bl.zquez | 2008-03-27 19:23:49 +0000 (Thu, 27 Mar 2008) | 3 lines

libvortex:
* [fix] Updating regression tests (copyright).

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r752 | francis.brosnan.bl.zquez | 2008-03-24 22:39:28 +0000 (Mon, 24 Mar 2008) | 7 lines

libvortex:
* [fix] Fixed bug inside vortex connection creation when timeout
  activated, causing to lock the caller until consume all the timeout
  for hosts refusing the connection rather than failing soon.
  Missing connection status check before receiving wrong greetings
  reply. Reported by Jens Alfke (1.0/1.1).

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r751 | francis.brosnan.bl.zquez | 2008-03-24 19:08:17 +0000 (Mon, 24 Mar 2008) | 17 lines

libvortex:
* [fix] Fixed wrong handling at TLS profile implementation causing
  to not properly recover during TLS failures (TLS protocol handshake). 
  Fixed memory leak (error reply frame for TLS implementation wasn't
  released). (1.0/1.1).

* [fix] Making vortex client side implemetation for TLS profile to
  not unref the connection on protocol failure. Rather, return the
  reference to the user the let the application space to implement
  its error handling (1.0/1.1). 

* [fix] Updated vortex_connection_set_auto_tls documentation to include
  more references about its function (1.0/1.1).

* [fix] Fixed vortex_tls_start_negociation_sync to return a reference
  to the connection received if a timeout is found (1.0/1.1).

