------------------------------------------------------------------------
r662 | francis.brosnan.bl.zquez | 2008-02-07 18:12:39 +0000 (Thu, 07 Feb 2008) | 7 lines

libvortex:
* [fix] Fixing bug inside out of order reply handling which
  wasn't rechecking the next seq-no value to use, making the vortex
  engine to produce reply frames using the same seq-no values, 
  causing the remote peer to drop the connection due to a protocol
  violation.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
