r422 | francis.brosnan.bl.zquez | 2007-09-30 10:33:56 +0000 (Sun, 30 Sep 2007) | 14 lines

libafdal:
* [new] General update to remove the last depedency with glib:
  afdal event source and afdal event process modules. These are
  now replaced by a generic and configurable implementation that
  allows to perform the same tasks, with default handlers, but
  at the same time configurable to keep working with gtk+ 
  applications. Module afdal process added, with API:

   - afdal_process_launch
   - afdal_process_launch_no_thread
   - afdal_process_set
   - (AfDalProcessLaunchFunc) 
   - (AfDalProcessFunc)

