r191 | francis.brosnan.bl.zquez | 2007-06-19 11:08:28 +0000 (Tue, 19 Jun 2007) | 15 lines

libafgs:
* [new] Updated afgs database module to include a new abstract service that
  allows to check the connection created, allowing the module to perform checks
  before executing an SQL command. Using this feature now the afgs layer is able
  to resume after a database restart (currently only postgresql).

* [fix] General update to remove gint, gchar, gboolean and gpointer types replacing
  them with the default types: int, char, bool and axlPointer.

* [fix] Fixed several minor memory leaks.

* [fix] Updated afgs config module internals to use axlHash type rather than GTree.

* [fix] Updated afgs log module to using fopen API rather than the Glib API.

