r34 | francis.brosnan.bl.zquez | 2007-04-05 20:08:07 +0000 (Thu, 05 Apr 2007) | 28 lines

libvortex:
* [new] Added new module to implement a portable threading API, supporting
  initially POSIX and windows API. The new API includes basic support to create
  threads, support for mutex and support for conditional vars. Replaced all
  calls to previous api g_mutex_*, g_thread_* and g_cond*.
  Checked that the result properly executes the regression test.
  API added:

   - VortexThread (type)
   - vortex_thread_create
   - VortexThreadConf (enum)
   - VortexMutex (type)
   - vortex_mutex_create
   - vortex_mutex_destroy
   - vortex_mutex_lock
   - vortex_mutex_unlock
   - VortexCond (type)
   - vortex_cond_create
   - vortex_cond_signal
   - vortex_cond_broadcast
   - vortex_cond_wait
   - vortex_cond_timedwait
   - vortex_cond_destroy

* [fix] Replaced all calls to the g_static_mutex* api with new API provided.

* [fix] Removed vortex semaphore modules. It is no longer required.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
