r26 | francis.brosnan.bl.zquez | 2007-04-02 10:48:33 +0000 (Mon, 02 Apr 2007) | 15 lines

libcoyote:
* [fix] Reimplemented escaping chars code, to avoid using 
  g_strstr to check if an string has escapable chars and g_strsplit
  to escape characters. 

  Previous implementation was escaping characters already escaped
  and reporting strings to be escaped which wasn't required.
  
  Added a regression test to check the new implementation.

* [new] Added a new function that allows to get the number of
  escapable characters. API added:

   - coyote_xml_count_escape_chars

